The paper deals with compressed sensing, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The focus is on signal recovery on manifolds, which is a problem in machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a convex optimization algorithm, which is a common technique in numerical analysis (cs.NA) and multimedia (cs.MM).
